### 3. **WhatsApp Alerts (Webhook Integration)**
**User Story:**
As an India-based user, I want to receive WhatsApp alerts for large transactions so that I catch fraud immediately.

**Acceptance Criteria:**
- Set custom alert threshold ($100+/₹8000+)
- Receive alert within 2 minutes of transaction upload
- Click alert to view transaction details on web

**Effort:** S (2–3 days)

**Why Now:**
- India market insight: WhatsApp > Email for alerts
- Builds on Razorpay relationship (they have WhatsApp SDK)
- Low-hanging fruit: reuse transaction processing pipeline

**Tech Approach:**
```typescript
// lib/whatsappClient.ts
import { Client } from 'twilio';

export async function sendTransactionAlert(
  phoneNumber: string,
  transaction: Transaction
): Promise<void> {
  const twilio = new Client(process.env.TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID, process.env.TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN);

  await twilio.messages.create({
    from: 'whatsapp:+1234567890',
    to: `whatsapp:${phoneNumber}`,
    body: `🚨 Large transaction: ₹${transaction.amount} to ${transaction.description}. Confirm: [link]`,
  });
}

// Trigger in /api/transactions/process
if (transaction.amount > userThreshold) {
  await sendTransactionAlert(user.whatsapp_phone, transaction);
}
```

